@section Database schema reference

The full schema lives in @file{sql/001_init.sql}.  Migrations after
that point are Java classes under
@file{src/main/precompiled/ai/ownsona/migrations/}.

@subsection The @code{memories} table

Documented per-column in @ref{The memories table}.

@subsection Indexes (current shape)

@multitable @columnfractions .35 .15 .50
@headitem Index @tab Type @tab Purpose
@item @code{memories_user_id_idx} @tab B-tree @tab Per-user filter.
@item @code{memories_created_at_idx} @tab B-tree @tab Listing newest first.
@item @code{memories_deleted_at_idx} @tab B-tree @tab Tombstone filter.
@item @code{memories_tags_idx} @tab GIN @tab Tag filter on @code{tags}.
@item @code{memories_text_trgm_idx} @tab GIN @tab Trigram for @code{text_search}.
@item @code{memories_embedding_idx} @tab HNSW @tab Cosine-similarity recall.
@item @code{memories_unique_normalized_active} @tab Unique partial @tab Exact-duplicate prevention.
@end multitable

@subsection The @code{db_version} table

Created by @code{DbMigrator} on first startup.

@multitable @columnfractions .25 .25 .50
@headitem Column @tab Type @tab Purpose
@item @code{version} @tab @code{INT PRIMARY KEY} @tab Migration's target version.
@item @code{applied_at} @tab @code{TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()} @tab When it ran.
